  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will train participants (young people and older adults) to do a visual task, and&#xD;
      will assess whether this results in changes in behavioral assessments. In some participants,&#xD;
      we will be also testing whether MRI measures (cortical thickness, functional connectivity)&#xD;
      change with training.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
